                {{else}}
                    <a href="http://{{host}}.{{subdomain}}/#/users/reset-password/{{resetToken}}">{{host}}.{{subdomain}}/#/users/reset-password/{{resetToken}}</a><br />
                {{/if}}
                    If you didn't requested to change your login/password, or did it by accident, just ignore this email. 
